<script>
import BlogPost from '../components/testBlog'

export default {
  components: {
    BlogPost
  },
  data() {
    return {
      posts: [
        { id: 1, title: 'My journey with Vue', content: "hello" },
        { id: 2, title: 'Blogging with Vue' },
        { id: 3, title: 'Why Vue is so fun' }
      ]
    }
  }
}
</script>

<template>
  <BlogPost v-for="post in posts" :key="post.id" :title="post.title" :content="post.content"></BlogPost>
</template>
